===聲調===

雖然顾赛芬認為北京話已經沒有獨立入聲調<ref name="Couvreur 1907 p. ">{{cite book | last=Couvreur | first=S. | title=Guide de la conversation, français-anglais-chinois | publisher=Imprimerie de la Mission Catholoque | year=1907 | url=https://books.google.com/books?id=5xhJAQAAMAAJ | language=fr | access-date=2022-06-09 | page=}}</ref>，但其依然將入聲獨立標記，因此共有[[陰平|陰平]]、[[陽平|陽平]]、[[上聲|上聲]]、[[去聲|去聲]]、[[入聲|入聲]]五個聲調<ref name="Couvreur 1911 p. "/>。

